title: Marizu - I Know
seo_description: Why should you fear when you know God is by your side always? In this beautiful song, the Uk based Nigerian says a prayer to God. confirming his knowledge of the fact that he knows God is here, so he should not be worried or despaired.
description: Why should you fear when you know God is by your side always? In this beautiful song, the Uk based Nigerian says a prayer to God. confirming his knowledge of the fact that he knows God is here, so he should not be worried or despaired. Have you ever wondered if God is even listening to your prayers? then listen to this song with intentions. God bless you!!!
